{"tid":1393803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【聲明】渣哥 一九九六: 無言感激 但不會接受任何捐款","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f60713c503559ba861496e035382ddc57b6dea90","tid":1393803,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:05:59.000Z","msg":"【聲明】<br />\n自宣布推出免費食物行動後，收到大量留言，絕大部分都是讚好，支持，鼓勵，足以証明決定正確，暖暖在心頭，無言感激🙏🙏🙏<br />\n<br />\n但亦有小部分不滿的，留言惡意中傷，誹謗，甚至乎話要到店亂取食物，搗亂，人身攻擊等等，有些留言內容更不堪入目。<br />\n<br />\n事情其實非常簡單，作為一個普通香港人，知悉有年輕人沒有食物，擔心佢地餓壞身體，主動請佢地食少少嘢，實屬小事一樁。<br />\n<br />\n任何人要講乜，甚至做乜，悉隨尊便！<br />\n不滿意的，因為不想浪費時間，<br />\n所以我們的回應亦只此一次 :<br />\n【人為善，福雖未至，禍必遠離】 <br />\n【人為惡，禍雖未至，福必遠離】<br />\n<br />\n渣哥 一九九六<br />\n<br />\n**Memo紙，未必能夠如數貼出，會收藏作為留念，希望大家包容。<br />\n**再強調，我們不會接受任何捐款。"},{"pid":"c7c4147aa095d63d10926e9b726b61591530e1d9","tid":1393803,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"【天使，魔鬼】<br />\n【圖1】<br />\n你班友真係話極都唔聽，各分店都已不斷婉拒你地放低錢！<br />\n你地仲係要放低就走左去，店員就要即追，你睇現場環境，出到門口，你應該已經大概去到北角！<br />\n仲話有個望落肥嘟嘟，但跑得快過保特，唔知以為佢搶左野...<br />\n懲教署人員劈低走左去又有...<br />\n仲有林林總總既方法，誓死不休係要放低錢先安樂...！<br />\n<br />\n#佢仲話身在圍牆內心在雞蛋中<br />\n#我就真係又俾你地整到眼濕濕勒<br />\n<br />\n嗱，真係要乖乖地，聽我講<br />\n1 我地講得好清楚，不會接受任何捐款，饋贈，小費...等等<br />\n2 我地暫時仲有足夠能力應付，但可以答應大家，到唔够錢有需要時，一定會通知大家，到時就任你俾！<br />\n3 我清楚知道，瞭解，明白大家好有心，但其實仲有好多渠道架，問下留意下就知架勒！<br />\n<br />\n【圖2】<br />\n俾大家當消閒娛樂笑下🤣<br />\n兩名加埋都應該超過100歲既大嬸，死話自己係年青人，店員怕佢煩照俾，佢地死話要每人2盒攞走，店員話你食完一盒先一盒，佢地就發爛咋，店員怕事，俾左佢。<br />\n<br />\n#原來人格只值26蚊x2<br />\n<br />\n1 已吩附店員要企硬，假既就1條毛都唔會再俾！<br />\n2 其實已寫得好清楚，店員係有最終決定權！<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有心人，天不負，<br />\n臥薪嘗膽，三千越甲氣呑吳！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n💛大家加油，香港加油💪🏻"},{"pid":"b346e02ee5ae5563944d4caf9f987fc153a98954","tid":1393803,"uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67362815_2384295638315130_6673504280260902912_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_oc=AQkomQIUZbh8BMxeo6FZBXrm88tSnzZo0t7c_kpbywOuOXhQLZhYNgytlpcT-5dnXns&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=4e2369519ec7e922de716fbb226ce6fe&amp;oe=5DE52CC5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67362815_2384295638315130_6673504280260902912_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_oc%3DAQkomQIUZbh8BMxeo6FZBXrm88tSnzZo0t7c_kpbywOuOXhQLZhYNgytlpcT-5dnXns%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D4e2369519ec7e922de716fbb226ce6fe%26oe%3D5DE52CC5&h=157ad701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/68555062_2384295668315127_3858127757166772224_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQlsztiSRpoZ4Ar6JZOOn1pg__-tOoIY-w7H_Xpr6Zi794Ug39yAFHPemgcShGKmsQ0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=2d2b8d527cd6533fe8b5fbfaeee1d9ad&amp;oe=5DD863DE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F68555062_2384295668315127_3858127757166772224_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQlsztiSRpoZ4Ar6JZOOn1pg__-tOoIY-w7H_Xpr6Zi794Ug39yAFHPemgcShGKmsQ0%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D2d2b8d527cd6533fe8b5fbfaeee1d9ad%26oe%3D5DD863DE&h=a6df2064&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a1fbed7f24c8d1ca50773debbcaddc29432d6a5","tid":1393803,"uid":229134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:50:30.000Z","msg":"我哋其他人咪多啲用正價幫趁，又或者見到年輕人幫佢哋即場加餸。"},{"pid":"2f7d08688fbb9430d7ce04afb33e0eb61c66bc3d","tid":1393803,"uid":214588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"香港人生活節奏咁快 買完野仲等佢地找錢咩 比完就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4630dcc502086003a390e55b6ca45101f7650ae8","tid":1393803,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:59:19.000Z","msg":"唔使找唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e45d53b7c4795d153e1c7d1ff1bbdb9cc1ace2","tid":1393803,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"已經叫咗返九龍灣既fd 幫襯多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258001effbaa6945ceff3263fd333dc570674962","tid":1393803,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"CWB 同九龍灣係同一間??"},{"pid":"74003b672829b07343c8cc5e0662c7206aa11a44","tid":1393803,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4b9729c84f1901711137ff7d6a4b5fa27fbf978","tid":1393803,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"258001effbaa6945ceff3263fd333dc570674962","tid":1393803,"uid":166792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:27.000Z","msg":"CWB 同九龍灣係同一間??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:17:41.000Z","msg":"三間分店 --- 銅鑼灣，德福，東涌"},{"pid":"96df1871b31af198cbd861f25defabb28e1b2835","tid":1393803,"uid":59971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"雖然貴左d 不過下次支持下"},{"pid":"5cec5a9d51483869cadff293b5d407118420fadc","tid":1393803,"uid":279201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"良心"},{"pid":"410dabdbba8a90d2b6d78eafa17202cf48e6076b","tid":1393803,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"真。香港人"}]}